data.description: Historic home + single wide trailer on 5.29 unrestricted acres! The main home exudes historic charm with real wood flooring, historic details, and designated rooms. A light color palette lends itself to many colors and decor. The main home features all new Andersen premium windows, new washer, dryer, water softener, water heater & refrigerator, all included with the home. The 920 sq ft mobile home has Energy Star rating from manufacturer, includes a new water heater as well. It features 2 beds and 2 baths. 2013 year model. No restrictions on this property. Horses are welcome! Minutes from new Samsung plant & proposed Ronald Reagan expansion from I-35 to hwy.95. Easy access to Granger Lake and toll roads without traffic headaches. Come swing on the porch and listen to nothing, except the birds. Conventional loan and cash accepted.
